nodes.text: An unidentified Neimoidian was present at the Battle of Muunilinst. The Neimoidian oversaw the battle along with other Muuns via hologram. He was captured along with San Hill and the other Muuns after Obi-Wan Kenobi and the Muunilinst 10 secured the InterGalactic Banking Clan's command center. After he was arrested, he held the robe a Muun while being taken onto a Republic cruiser.
The Hyperspace Avatars state that this Neimoidian is Nute Gunray, but Leland Chee has said he's never been named. He is the only Neimoidian to have appeared in the series.
This Neimoidian wears the same purple drape and miter to that of Rune Haako in Attack of the Clones.
